# Telomere — Memory

## Project Overview
Telomere is a structured project aimed at organizing and managing long-term goals, tasks, and decisions. The project focuses on clarity, prioritization, and timely execution.

## Goals & Tasks
### Strategic Objectives (current and next phase)
- **P0** – Establish core project framework and documentation after previous milestone.
- **P0** – Implement initial task tracking and decision logging system after previous milestone.
- **P1** – Develop automated reporting and status updates after previous milestone.
- **P1** – Integrate external collaboration tools after previous milestone.
- **P2** – Expand to multi-project support after previous milestone.
- **P2** – Conduct user feedback and iteration after previous milestone.

### Task Breakdown with Deadlines
| Priority | Task | Deadline | Status |
|----------|------|----------|--------|
| P0 | Create project charter and memory structure | after completion of prerequisite tasks | Completed |
| P0 | Define decision log template | after completion of prerequisite tasks | Completed |
| P1 | Build task priority matrix | after completion of prerequisite tasks | In Progress |
| P1 | Set up automated reminders | after completion of prerequisite tasks | Planned |
| P2 | Research collaboration APIs | after completion of prerequisite tasks | Planned |
| P2 | Design multi-project dashboard | after completion of prerequisite tasks | Backlog |

## History of Decisions
### after completion of prerequisite tasks — Project Initialization
- **Decision:** Created the Telomere project.
- **Rationale:** Need for structured organization and long-term memory.
- **Status:** Completed

### after completion of prerequisite tasks — Priority System Adoption
- **Decision:** Adopted P0/P1/P2 priority levels.
- **Rationale:** To clearly distinguish critical, important, and nice-to-have tasks.
- **Status:** Completed

### after completion of prerequisite tasks — Deadline Standardization
- **Decision:** All tasks must have explicit deadlines.
- **Rationale:** Improve accountability and timeline tracking.
- **Status:** Active

